title: Annyeong, Jeonwoochi! Dosoolrobotdaegyeoljeon
synopsis: Jeon Woo-chi travels over 500 years into the year 2015 on the elevator after defeating a king who bullies his people. He meets Suk and San-cho, two kids who are masters at martial arts and they become friends. In the meantime, Jeon Woo-chi's friend and rival Woo Dang-tang and the king join forces to take revenge on Jeon Woo-chi. They even make a martial arts robot.
